<p style="text-align: center;">Each year, Montserrat College of Art invites art educators nationwide to submit work for our annual summer exhibition.</p>

<p style="text-align: center;"><span>This year, due to COVID-19, we will be offering an online gallery experience along with a guest Juror to present awards, give an artist talk, and have a Q+A session to participants.</span></p>

